Title: Sisodia is the first accused in the liquor scam, but Kejriwal is the mastermind.
Narrative: Union minister Anurag Thakur claimed on Saturday that Delhi deputy chief minister Manish Sisodia is an accused number one in the national capital's alleged liquor scam, but that the kingpin is chief minister Arvind Kejriwal.
Interest: manish sisodia, anurag kashyap, aap, arvind kejriwal
